{"tid":2073701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗：維護國家安全公署並非基本法22條所指「中央各部門」","createTime":"2020-06-21T13:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T14:21:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"34ae3d87769b621d47df6fbae719846d64c238e0","tid":2073701,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:39:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1533307\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1533307&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=dd22c9dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1533307&h=2a0dc6dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1533307</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委譚耀宗表示，中央政府在港的「維護國家安全公署」，是特別設立的機構，並非《基本法》22條所指的中央各部門。<br />\n<br />\n被問到由特首任主席的「維護國家安全委員會」，有由中央政府指派國安事務顧問，如果意見與其他委員有分歧如何處理，譚耀宗說，不要低估安全委員會成員的智慧，應該可以妥善解決，既能照顧中央想法，亦能兼顧香港的實際情況。<br />\n<br />\n至於為何由特首指定審理國安案件的法官人選，譚耀宗說，法官任命有好多不同意見，包括有人提議要由中國籍法官審理，不容許外籍法官審理有關案件等，他認為雖然草案提出的安排，與現時法官任命由專責委員會推薦，再由特首任命的做法不同，但同樣由特首任命，因此認為不會牴觸《基本法》和切實可行，相信不會對現職法官構成壓力。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，草案內容已結合香港實際情況、《憲法》、《基本法》和全國人大的決定，參考和聽取好多香港的意見，希望通過後令香港人有信心，亦令香港社會可以穩定。<br />\n<br />\n同樣有份出席常委會會議的基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠表示，「維護國家安全公署」的職能與中聯辦不同，但工作人員同時要遵守香港和內地的法律，其他詳情有待草案公布再解釋。"},{"pid":"ef64bb2200f06be2ba7ce5fdbffb3612cce14d2b","tid":2073701,"uid":292644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實廿二條到底包咩郜門</span>"},{"pid":"1d8388cfdda67c6c2dced402f9ffa46f1333da17","tid":2073701,"uid":262191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ef64bb2200f06be2ba7ce5fdbffb3612cce14d2b","tid":2073701,"uid":292644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實廿二條到底包咩郜門</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003175149d06b700672d5934e69d9e88bb765472","tid":2073701,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/a3/KkbnN.gif/revision/latest/top-crop/width/150/height/150?cb=20110710090638\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fa%2Fa3%2FKkbnN.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Ftop-crop%2Fwidth%2F150%2Fheight%2F150%3Fcb%3D20110710090638&h=ffb63d98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88e079ab03a3bc829933de5779a03839bdc72ccb","tid":2073701,"uid":105538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"是旦啦<br />\n<br />\n快啲通過！<br />\n<br />\n唔過正契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51604abd39225d042b08453183ffd415fae34c37","tid":2073701,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef64bb2200f06be2ba7ce5fdbffb3612cce14d2b","tid":2073701,"uid":292644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實廿二條到底包咩郜門</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:48:12.000Z","msg":"基本法解釋權喺人大常委會度<br />\n所以條文幾多條，寫乜都唔重要<br />\n佢地話係就係，唔係就唔係"},{"pid":"0540fa5663fbc8868c0d37e4a48c496da40d3501","tid":2073701,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"總之就唔好撚再縮沙"},{"pid":"72992dc6f8b68b521e343927c3595774940c8ea2","tid":2073701,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"我要真野，成日放fake news玩我地有咩意思，佢自己咩都唔知係到鳩估，呢隻譚耀宗。"},{"pid":"8007eebdd5026db486ac394b14e650692a2b534f","tid":2073701,"uid":357710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34ae3d87769b621d47df6fbae719846d64c238e0","tid":2073701,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T1